onclusion We have presented a novel technique that leverages neural audio codecs for creative granular resynthesis, enabling high fidelity, versatile, no-training timbre transfer. By operating in the latent space of pre-trained codecs, our approach achieves smooth timbral blending while preserving the structural characteristics of target audio signals. In essence, we are", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
